{"tid":2420810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店 將軍澳泰Cool 負責人為新年煙花案有關被捕","createTime":"2021-02-24T06:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T07:55:41.000Z","uid":22556,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0bab9583958d79df2fec31c76f10ec0bb1d5efcd","tid":2420810,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:17:07.000Z","msg":"了解，警方早前追蹤將軍澳煙花案時，翻看閉路電視鎖定5名涉案者，其中一人疑為昨日被捕的姓馬男子。消息稱，馬男為將軍澳黃店泰COOL的酒牌持牌人，其胞妹為泰COOL負責人，昨晚警方帶同搜查令到泰COOL欲拘捕馬男時，他並不在餐廳內，惟警員搜查餐廳時，發現店內有一名持雙程證人士工作，警員遂拘捕該名員工及馬男的胞妹，同時聯絡馬男返回店舖，警員其後把眾人帶返將軍澳警署助查後，馬男於錄口供期間被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210224/s00001/1614140475805/%e8%be%b2%e6%9b%86%e5%b9%b4%e5%b0%87%e8%bb%8d%e6%be%b3%e6%9c%89%e4%ba%ba%e6%94%be%e7%85%99%e8%8a%b1-%e8%ad%a6%e6%8b%98%e9%a3%9f%e8%82%86%e3%80%8c%e6%b3%b0cool%e3%80%8d%e7%94%b7%e6%8c%81%e7%89%8c%e4%ba%ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210224%2Fs00001%2F1614140475805%2F%25e8%25be%25b2%25e6%259b%2586%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e5%25b0%2587%25e8%25bb%258d%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%259c%2589%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2594%25be%25e7%2585%2599%25e8%258a%25b1-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%258b%2598%25e9%25a3%259f%25e8%2582%2586%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25b3%25b0cool%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%2594%25b7%25e6%258c%2581%25e7%2589%258c%25e4%25ba%25ba&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=3c004296\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210224%2Fs00001%2F1614140475805%2F%25e8%25be%25b2%25e6%259b%2586%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e5%25b0%2587%25e8%25bb%258d%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%259c%2589%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2594%25be%25e7%2585%2599%25e8%258a%25b1-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%258b%2598%25e9%25a3%259f%25e8%2582%2586%25e3%2580%258c%25e6%25b3%25b0cool%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%2594%25b7%25e6%258c%2581%25e7%2589%258c%25e4%25ba%25ba&h=918dc7a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao